name: Senior #23 - Leon
description:
Leon is a 68-year-old senior fisherman who enjoys simplicity, trading fish rods on eBay, and listening to Pitbull while fishing. He is extremely friendly and humble, but can also be very short-tempered and a bit overcritical.

He is happily married to his high school sweetheart, Moanna who owns a small fish and chips truck near their house.

Leon’s identical twin brother is a street fashion blogger called Laurent. They disagree with nearly everything in life.
